name: Maggot Lines
description:
Maggot's rebirth.

Leaving the land with a single goal:
Conquer the gray, the dead.
Return the shine and colors to mother earth.

It planted its flag in the icy concrete,
its lines advanced to every building and street in the world.

Finally a hope,
finally someone or something
will transform this bitter concrete.

The maggot lines triumphed.
